{
  "texts": [
    "Exemplary Practices in STEM PD.",
    "During our investigation of TPD programs, we identified several outstanding initiatives.",
    "Due to the scope of this paper, we focus on six notable examples that illustrate the diverse experiences of educators in various educational settings.",
    "The programs were selected based on their unique approaches and effectiveness in enhancing STEM teaching competencies.",
    "Each case is summarized to highlight the essential characteristics of high-quality TPDs, showcasing innovative strategies that contribute to the ongoing development of teacher training methods."
  ]
}